  keywords  = {algorithm,Algorithms,article,artificial intelligence,Artificial intelligence,Artificial Intelligence,Behavioral research,classification,Classification (of information),classifier,Commerce,Communication,Computational intelligence,consumer attitude,Consumer Behavior,Consumer decision journey,Data Collection,Data streams,decision making,Decision making,Decision Making,electronic commerce,female,Female,human,Humans,information processing,Intelligent computing,Internet,interpersonal communication,Knowledge extraction,Learning algorithms,linguistics,machine learning,Machine learning,male,Male,marketing,Marketing,natural language processing,Natural language processing,NAtural language processing,Natural language processing systems,priority journal,procedures,Purchasing,Sales,shopping,social media,Social media,Social networking (online),Text analytics}
